00:00:06.835 --> 00:00:10.902
Let us prepare Til Mawa Burfi which is the main sweet of winters.

00:00:11.246 --> 00:00:16.968
Let us see what are the ingredients we require to prepare Til Mawa Burfi.

00:00:17.562 --> 00:00:19.276
Til (Sesame seeds) - 2 Cups.

00:00:20.119 --> 00:00:21.969
Sugar - 1 and half cup

00:00:22.797 --> 00:00:25.607
Crumbled mawa (Dried Milk) - 1 Cup.

00:00:26.141 --> 00:00:27.879
Cashew - 2 to 3 tablespoonful

00:00:28.717 --> 00:00:34.421
Roast Til in the kadhai to prepare Til Mawa Burfi.

00:00:37.902 --> 00:00:39.299
Heat the kadhai.

00:00:42.581 --> 00:00:56.667
Roast Til in it till it turns brown.

00:00:57.008 --> 00:01:01.453
Don’t make the till dark brown because it might get bitter in taste.

00:01:06.129 --> 00:01:12.834
The colour of Til has changed and it has also expanded.

00:01:16.337 --> 00:01:18.856
It is now ready.

00:01:24.752 --> 00:01:28.323
Grind it into a coarse powder after cooling it.

00:01:32.293 --> 00:01:34.348
We have made a coarse powder of Til.

00:01:34.484 --> 00:01:37.391
Let us roast Mawa now.

00:01:39.934 --> 00:01:41.220
Take Mawa in a Kadhai.

00:01:45.861 --> 00:01:50.087
Roast the Mawa till it turns light brown.

00:01:51.384 --> 00:01:55.828
It should not burn from where it touches the surface.

00:01:58.595 --> 00:02:01.717
Ghee is separated from the Mawa and it has turned light brown.

00:02:02.086 --> 00:02:03.784
Mawa is ready now.

00:02:11.919 --> 00:02:13.255
Let us prepare the Chashni (sugar syrup) now.

00:02:14.024 --> 00:02:20.230
Take 1 and a half cup of sugar in a Kadhai.

00:02:20.954 --> 00:02:23.025
Add ¾ cup water in it.

00:02:34.524 --> 00:02:36.865
Boil the sugar till it dissolves in water.

00:02:37.168 --> 00:02:40.720
Boil the solution for two more minutes and check it after that.

00:02:44.257 --> 00:02:48.431
Cut the cashew till the time the solution boils.

00:02:52.018 --> 00:02:54.852
Make 3-4 pieces of a cashew.

00:02:58.938 --> 00:03:04.021
Stir the solution of sugar and water in between.

00:03:05.620 --> 00:03:12.300
Sugar is dissolved properly and we will check it after boiling it for 2 more minutes.

00:03:16.497 --> 00:03:27.450
Take one or two drops of Chasni in a bowl and try to test it within your fingers.

00:03:31.655 --> 00:03:34.739
Boil it for 1 more minute.

00:03:36.082 --> 00:03:38.145
Let us check the Chashni once again.

00:03:40.657 --> 00:03:46.884
take one or two drops of chasni in a bowl and try to test it within yours fingers.

00:03:47.132 --> 00:03:49.513
The wires are forming in the Chashni.

00:03:50.359 --> 00:04:01.605
It will form 2 wires when it is cooled.

00:04:02.031 --> 00:04:06.141
The Chashni is now ready.

00:04:06.709 --> 00:04:08.297
Turn off the flame now.

00:04:12.732 --> 00:04:14.851
Add the powder of Til in the Chasni.

00:04:26.405 --> 00:04:27.731
Add cashew in it .

00:04:32.728 --> 00:04:36.549
Mix Mawa in it when the mixture is cooled.

00:04:38.989 --> 00:04:41.362
wait till it cool down.

00:04:42.422 --> 00:04:44.581
The mixture is cooled now.

00:04:48.357 --> 00:04:51.255
Mix Mawa in it.

00:05:09.991 --> 00:05:14.264
Spread some oil on a Thali.

00:05:14.631 --> 00:05:16.742
Spread some oil on a Thali.

00:05:26.929 --> 00:05:31.279
Spread it uniformly with the help of a spoon.

00:05:34.326 --> 00:05:36.334
We have frozen the mixture on the Thali.

00:05:36.479 --> 00:05:41.924
Cut in into pieces after 1 hour.

00:05:44.827 --> 00:05:49.216
Til Mawa Burfi is now ready and we will cut it into pieces.

00:05:59.106 --> 00:06:02.281
We can also cut it into the shape of diamonds.

00:06:07.161 --> 00:06:11.931
Take out the pieces of Burfi on a plate.

